title: WHERE IS RANKED 5'S AND RANKED 3'S?
body: Aye rito, where are those ranked que's? I just played ranked teams last night but they aren't an option right now??

replies.body: Yeah, ranked teams are on a set schedule depending on the region, and weekend/weekday.  The full schedule is available at our[ ranked team schedule](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/209964886-Ranked-Teams-Schedule) guide.  Hope that helps!
